OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy night, with showers
OL,7,Ffairly isolated at first but becoming
OL,8,Fmore frequent and widespread towards
OL,9,Fmidnight, continuing through the
OL,10,Fevening and early hours. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA mixture of sunny spells
OL,13,Fand blustery showers, these perhaps
OL,14,Fheavy and thundery at times. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
